<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>LETTER OF AUTHORIZATION TO REMOVE</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            size: a4;
            margin: 0.5in;
        }

        .loar-container {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #000;
            background: white;
            margin: 0;
            /* padding: 20px; */
            line-height: 1.2;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 40px);
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .header {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .header-top-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: stretch;
            padding-inline: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            min-height: 60px;
        }

        .header-title {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            padding-right: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .header-title h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #000;
            line-height: 1.0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .header .metadata {
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            font-size: 8pt;
            text-align: right;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-left: 15px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: normal;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .header-bottom-row {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header .disclaimer {
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-style: normal;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .date-field {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .date-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .date-label {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 60px;
        }

        .date-input {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 150px;
            height: 18px;
            margin-left: -20px;
        }

        .dod-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-left: 150px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .decorative-bar {
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #000;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .recipient-section {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .to-section,
        .from-section {
            flex: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .to-label,
        .from-label {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 9pt;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            z-index: 1;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 0 5px;
        }

        .to-box,
        .from-box {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 10px;
            min-height: 80px;
            background-color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .to-box .content,
        .from-box .content {
            font-size: 8pt;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .authorization-section {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .authorization-section .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 200px;
            height: 16px;
            margin: 0 3px;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }

        .authorization-section .transportation-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .authorization-section .transportation-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            width: 300px;
            min-height: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
            padding: 2px 0;
        }

        .authorization-section .transportation-label {
            font-weight: normal;
            font-size: 8pt;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            display: block;
            text-align: left;
            clear: both;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .authorization-section .continuation-text {
            display: inline;
            vertical-align: bottom;
            margin-left: 5px;
            flex-shrink: 1;
        }

        .property-list-section {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .property-list-header {
            background-color: #d0d0d0;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 9pt;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .property-list-content {
            padding: 8px;
            min-height: 80px;
        }

        .property-item {
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-size: 8pt;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .workload-list {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .workload-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 120px;
        }

        .workload-input {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 150px;
            height: 16px;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }

        .horizontal-bar {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .instructions-section {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 8pt;
        }

        .instructions-section .highlight {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #000;
        }

        .email-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 250px;
            height: 16px;
            margin: 0 3px;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }

        .phone-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 150px;
            height: 16px;
            margin: 0 3px;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }

        .email-continuation,
        .phone-continuation {
            display: inline;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }

        .important-notes {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            line-height: 0.5;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 7pt;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .transportation-section {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .transportation-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
            margin-top: -5px !important;
            margin-left: 5px !important;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .transportation-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            margin: 5px 0;
            min-height: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            margin: 5px 0;
            min-height: 20px;
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 10px !important;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 300px;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }

        .signature-label {
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-top: -10px !important;
        }

        .gsa-transfer-order {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
        }

        .gsa-transfer-label {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="loar-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-top-row">
                <div class="header-title">
                    <h1>LETTER OF AUTHORIZATION TO REMOVE</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="metadata">
                    Prescribed by: DoD M 4160.21<br>
                    Sponsor: Disposition Services
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-bottom-row">
                <div class="disclaimer">This form may not be modified or altered. Other versions are not authorized.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Date Field -->
        <div class="date-field">
            <div class="date-section">
                <span class="date-label">Date:</span>
                <div class="date-input">
                    <% if (signatureDate) { %>
                        <%= new Date(signatureDate).toLocaleDateString('en-US') %>
                            <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dod-text">
                *For DOD releases, the individual signing must be listed on the LOA in the Centralized File*
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>

        <!-- Recipient and Sender Information -->
        <div class="recipient-section">
            <div class="to-section">
                <div class="to-label">To: DLA DISPOSITION SERVICES</div>
                <div class="to-box">
                    <div class="content">
                        <% if (propertyDetails && propertyDetails.length> 0) { %>
                            <% const sampleProperty=propertyDetails[0]; %>
                                <% if (sampleProperty.data && sampleProperty.data.propertyLocation) { %>
                                    <% const address=sampleProperty.data.propertyLocation; %>
                                        <%= address.line1 || '' %><br>
                                            <% if (address.line2) { %>
                                                <%= address.line2 %><br>
                                                    <% } %>
                                                        <% if (address.line3) { %>
                                                            <%= address.line3 %><br>
                                                                <% } %>
                                                                    <%= address.city || '' %>, <%= address.stateCode
                                                                            || '' %>
                                                                            <%= address.zip || '' %>
                                                                                <% } %>
                                                                                    <% } %>
                                                                                        <br><br>
                                                                                        <% if (propertyDetails &&
                                                                                            propertyDetails.length> 0)
                                                                                            { %>
                                                                                            <% const
                                                                                                sampleProperty=propertyDetails[0];
                                                                                                %>
                                                                                                <% if
                                                                                                    (sampleProperty.data
                                                                                                    &&
                                                                                                    sampleProperty.data.propertyPOC)
                                                                                                    { %>
                                                                                                    <% const
                                                                                                        poc=sampleProperty.data.propertyPOC;
                                                                                                        %>
                                                                                                        Phone: <%=
                                                                                                            poc.phone
                                                                                                            || '' %>
                                                                                                            <% } %>
                                                                                                                <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="from-section">
                <div class="from-label">From:</div>
                <div class="from-box">
                    <div class="content">
                        FOR DONEE: <%= request.doneeAccount?.name || '' %> - <%= request.doneeAccount?.organization?.name || '' %>
                        <br>
                            <% if (organizationMailingAddress?.address_line1) { %>
                                <%= organizationMailingAddress.address_line1 %>
                            <% } %>
                            <br>
                            <% if (organizationMailingAddress?.address_line2) { %>
                                <%= organizationMailingAddress.address_line2 %>
                            <% } %>
                            <br>
                            <% if (organizationMailingAddress?.city && organizationMailingAddress?.state && organizationMailingAddress?.postal_code) { %>
                                <%= organizationMailingAddress.city %>, <%= organizationMailingAddress.state %> <%= organizationMailingAddress.postal_code %>
                        <% } %>                                       
                        <% if (headAuthorizedUser) { %>
                            POC: <%= headAuthorizedUser.name %>
                            <br>
                            PHONE: <%= headAuthorizedOrganizationUser?.phoneNumber %>
                            <br>
                            EMAIL: <%= headAuthorizedUser.email %>
                        <% } else { %>
                            POC: <%= headAuthorizedUser.name %>
                            <br>
                            PHONE: <%= headAuthorizedOrganizationUser?.phoneNumber %>
                            <br>
                            EMAIL: <%= headAuthorizedUser.email %>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Authorization Statement -->
        <div class="authorization-section">
            <p>
                I, <span class="signature-line">
                    <%= saspUser?.name || '' %>
                </span>
                the undersigned, hereby authorize <br> <br>
            <div class="transportation-row">
                <span class="transportation-line">
                    <% if (shippingName) { %>
                        <%= shippingName %>
                            <% } %>
                </span>
                <span class="continuation-text">to remove the requisitions listed below on my behalf.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="transportation-label">PRINT NAME OF PERSON OR TRANSPORTATION COMPANY</div>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Signature Section -->
        <div class="signature-section">
            <span class="signature-label">SIGNATURE OF CUSTOMER:</span>
            <span class="signature-line">
                <% if (signatureDate && saspUser) { %>
                    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: flex-end;">
                        <div
                            style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: left; align-content: end; align-items: end; white-space: nowrap;">
                            <%= saspUser.name %>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-left: 30px;">
                            <small style="white-space: nowrap;">Digitally signed by <%= saspUser.name %><br>
                                    <% if (request.doneeAccount?.state?.stateName) { %>
                                        <%= request.doneeAccount.state.stateName %> SASP<br>
                                            <% } %>
                                                Date: <%= new Date(signatureDate).toLocaleString('en-US', {
                                                    year: 'numeric' , month: '2-digit' , day: '2-digit' ,
                                                    hour: '2-digit' , minute: '2-digit' , second: '2-digit' ,
                                                    timeZoneName: 'short' }) %>
                            </small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
            </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Property List Section -->
        <div class="property-list-section">
            <div class="property-list-header">Extent of Authority: To remove the property listed below.</div>
            <div class="property-list-content">
                <div
                    style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 9pt;">
                    <div style="flex: 1;">
                        LIST ITEM(S) by Requisition/DTID Number/Work Load List*:
                    </div>
                    <div class="gsa-transfer-order"
                        style="flex: 1; text-align: right; justify-content: flex-end; display: flex; font-size: 9pt;">
                        <span class="gsa-transfer-label">GSA Transfer Order # if applicable:</span>
                        <span class="gsa-transfer-value"><%= request.tcn || '' %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <% if (properties && properties.length> 0) { %>
                    <% properties.forEach(function(property, index) { %>
                        <% const propertyDetail=propertyDetails?.find(pd=> pd.data.itemControlNumber ===
                            property.property_control_number); %>
                            <div class="property-item">
                                <%= property.property_control_number %>
                                    <%= property.property_name || property.property_description || '' %>
                                        <% if (propertyDetail?.data?.fscCode) { %>
                                            FSC: <%= propertyDetail.data.fscCode %>, <%=
                                                    property.property_disposal_condition %> QTY <%=
                                                        property.property_allocated_quantity %>
                                                        <% } else { %>
                                                            QTY <%= property.property_allocated_quantity %>
                                                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                            <% }); %>
                                <% } %>

                                    <div class="workload-list">
                                        *Work Load List Number: _____________________________
                                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Horizontal Bar -->
        <div class="horizontal-bar"></div>

        <!-- Instructions Section -->
        <div class="instructions-section">
            <% if (propertyDetails && propertyDetails.length > 0) { %>
                <% const sampleProperty = propertyDetails[0]; %>
                <% if (sampleProperty.data && sampleProperty.data.propertyPOC) { %>
                    <% const poc = sampleProperty.data.propertyPOC; %>
                    <p>
                        PLEASE COMPLETE THIS FORM AND EMAIL OR FAX IT TO
                        <span class="email-line">
                            <%= poc.email %>
                        </span>
                    </p>
                    <% if (poc.fax) { %>
                    <p>
                        FAX: <%= poc.fax %>
                    </p>
                    <% } %>
                    <p>
                        PLEASE CALL <span class="phone-line">
                            <%= poc.phone %>
                        </span>
                        <span class="phone-continuation">TO SCHEDULE YOUR PICK-UP.</span>
                    </p>
                <% } %>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- Important Notes -->
        <div class="important-notes">
            <p>REMEMBER TO BRING ADEQUATE ID WHEN YOU COME</p>
            <p>THANK YOU</p>
            <p>******************************************************************</p>
            <p>PICK-UP OF REQUISITIONS IS REQUIRED WITHIN 14 DAYS OF THE 1348 DOCUMENT FOR DOD, LESO,</p>
            <p>FIRE FIGHTER, AND CFL CUSTOMERS AND 21 DAYS FOR ALL DONATION AND TRANSFER CUSTOMERS.</p>
            <p>ALL REQUISITIONS WILL BE CANCELLED AFTER THIS DATE.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <div>DLA FORM 2516, AUG 2017</div>
        <div style="font-weight: normal;">Page 1 of 1</div>
        <div>PDF (DLA)</div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
